{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, the author co-citation analysis conducted -using the WoS core collection -only focuses on the first author (Zupic and Čater 2015).",
    "To address this limitation, an additional step was taken to manually locate the referenced publications and include all the authors involved in those publications.",
    "On the other hand, it is important to note that for a pair of publications to be included in a co-citation network, they need to be cited with a certain frequency before being included in a co-citation network (Üsdiken and Pasadeos 1995).",
    "As a result, some of the newer publications may not have been considered in the analysis.",
    "The need for further research within the Business and Management field is underscored by the fact that the sample of the study included only 67 publications."
  ]
}